ry are confirmed by observations, the core mass\nfunction we predict can also serve to constrain core formation theories of\ngas-rich planets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 18:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 19:25:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-12"}
