ta}_{t,p, d}\\approx_d (\\mathsf{L}^{\\Delta}_{t,p,\n1})^d\\;\\text{ and }\\; \\mathsf{L}^{\\Delta}_{c,p, d}\\approx_d\n(\\mathsf{L}^{\\Delta}_{c,p, 1})^d.$$\n  All the previous results can be equally formulated for the $d$-torus\n$\\mathbb{T}^d$. We prove a de Leeuw type transference principle in the\nvector-valued setting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 19:03:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Jun 2021 07:59:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 May 2022 16:39:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-27"}
